<div style="margin-right: 2em;font-size: 1em;margin-bottom:1em;width:100%">
      <h2><a href="https://erlichlab.org/">Erlich Lab</a> (New York University Shanghai)</h2>
      
     <div class = "research-logo">
          <img src="/images/NYU_Shanghai_Logo.jpg" class="logo">
      </div>

      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-right: 1em;margin-bottom:-1em;">
      	 <p><b>Location:</b><br/>Shanghai, China</p>
      </div>
      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-bottom:-1em;">
      	 <p><b>Year:</b><br/>2018 - 2019</p>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
      
      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-right: 1em;margin-bottom:-1em;">
          <p><b>Subject:</b><br/>Description-Experience Gap:<br/> Animals and Humans</p>
      </div>
      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-bottom:-1em;">
      	<p><b>Role:</b><br/>Research Intern</p>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
      
      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-right: 1em;margin-bottom:-1em;">
      	<p><b>Team:</b>
         <ul>
         	<li>Rien Sonck </li>
            <li><a href="https://shanghai.nyu.edu/academics/faculty/directory/jeffrey-erlich">Prof. Dr. Jeffrey Erlich</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://shanghai.nyu.edu/academics/faculty/directory/evgeniya-lukinova">Dr. Evgeniya Lukinova</a></li>
         </ul>
          </p>
      </div>
      <div style="width: 40%; float:left;margin-bottom:-1em;">
      	<p><b>Code and Documents:</b>
         	<ul>
         		<li>GitHub: Coming soon</li>
         	</ul>
         </p>
      </div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
      <p style="text-align:justify;"><b>Description:</b><br/> The aim of this study is to investigate similarities and differences in decision-making across species. For this my lab developed a new risk-non-verbal task, adapted from Lukinova et al. (2019) delay-non-verbal task. The task mirrors the training procedure used with rodents in Erlich's lab.</p>
</div>
